WEBVTT

00:04.625 --> 00:05.875
Can we get a little help?

00:06.481 --> 00:07.360
Focus, fellas.

00:07.809 --> 00:09.030
We've got Pepsi!

00:09.413 --> 00:11.221
What if we just take like 15 minutes?

00:11.477 --> 00:12.354
Halfway through the game?

00:12.655 --> 00:13.335
They got Pepsi.

00:18.898 --> 00:20.087
So what do we call that?

00:20.345 --> 00:21.077
Halftime.

00:21.327 --> 00:22.406
I like halftime.

00:22.557 --> 00:25.479
Even the first halftime wasn't halftime without Pepsi.

00:25.689 --> 00:27.807
This halftime, catch Bruno Mars live.

00:28.049 --> 00:28.993
Brought to you by who else?

00:29.339 --> 00:29.735
Pepsi.

